Implementation sketch for push_existing (adds to src/learnings/crud/writer.rs from FEAT-001):
```rust
impl<'a> LearningWriter<'a> {
    /// Register an already-recorded learning for later embedding.
    /// Use when the DB insert happened outside this writer — e.g. merge_cluster
    /// which combines insert + bandit-stat updates in a single atomic tx and
    /// cannot route through `record()`.
    pub fn push_existing(&mut self, learning_id: i64, title: String, content: String) {
        if self.db_dir.is_some() {
            self.pending.push(PendingEmbed { learning_id, title, content });
        }
    }
}
```

